# FP Conglomerate — environment template
#
# Vite reads `.env` from EACH APP ROOT, not from the repo root:
#   - Copy `frontend/.env.example` → `frontend/.env` (marketing site)
#   - Copy `admin/.env.example`     → `admin/.env` (staff admin)
#
# Full deployment steps and where every value comes from:
#   docs/DEPLOYMENT.md
#
# The `elevate-backend/` folder here is reference-only — deploy the API separately.
